 "Reflection is a teaching method often used to \nconnect theory to practice. Reflection tasks often provide learners with an \nopportunity to observe and reflect on their observations before presenting \nthese as a piece of academic work. Journals, diaries, profiles and portfolios \nare useful tools for collecting observation data. Rubrics and guides can be \neffective feedback tools.": "A reflexi\u00f3n \u00e9 un m\u00e9todo de aprendizaxe usado frecuentemente para \nvincular a teoria \u00e1 pr\u00e1ctica. As tarefas de reflexi\u00f3n proporcionan a mi\u00fado aos alumnos \nunha oportunidade para observar e reflexionar sobre as s\u00faas observaci\u00f3ns antes de presentalas \ncomo unha peza do traballo acad\u00e9mico. Os xornais, diarios, perf\u00eds e os cartafoles \nson ferramentas \u00fatiles para recoller os datos da observaci\u00f3n. Os t\u00edtulos e guias poden \nser ferramentas de retroacci\u00f3n eficaces.", 
